To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Freedom of Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

Janet Przewlocki
 2846 N. 46th Ave Apt 5
Phoenix, AZ  85035
602-473-6789 or 480-292-4384
email janet.przewlocki@gmail.com

June 9, 2024

FOIA/Privacy Act Officer
US Department of Justice

Federal Bureau of Investigations
https://efoia.fbi.gov
or fax to 540-868-4997
/
FOIA/Privacy Act Officer
Department of Homeland Security
FOIA@HQ.DHS.gov

RE: PRIVACY ACT REQUEST UNDER 5 U.S.C. § 552a

To Whom It May Concern:

Pursuant to the Freedom of Information Act, I hereby request the following records:

To Whom It May Concern:

This is a request under the Freedom of Information Act. I hereby request the following records:

Please provide all notifications of ongoing Non- investigation subject(NIS), whether categorized as intelligence, counter-terrorism, criminal, civil, or otherwise, under National Security labels or otherwise, and/or all notifications of enrollment into covert community policing/crime prevention/neurological or psychological behavior modification programs, naming me--Janet Jo Przewlocki- personally as the person under scrutiny, investigation, or study, or as the person enrolled into any classified or unclassified programs of the kind detailed above, issued to any and all community members in the city and state of Phoenix, Arizona and all reasons for these notifications, from the time period as to when it started the invasion of my privacy and the destruction of my character. To my awareness it started 12 Dec, 2019  the present date of June 9, 2024 with specific information contained in the notifications, including the manner of labeling and characterizing of my person, the specific reason for the investigation/s/program enrollments, the duration of the investigation/program, the manner in which the investigation/program is being conducted, and the authorizing body or bodies permitting the investigation; if your agency would like to state that such notifications do not exist, or that no such ongoing investigation or program exists or has been initiated, please provide a clear and truthful statement to this effect.

(This FOIA request, while specific to my name and person Janet Jo Przewlocki, addresses the current general public concern regarding illegitimate investigations and surveillance targeted at all law-abiding citizens and residents, including myself, and will provide particular information of general public interest, to all members of the media and the public.)

The requested documents will be made available to the general public, and this request is not being made for commercial purposes.

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 20 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,
Janet Jo Przewlocki
 
Sincerely,

Janet Jo Przewlocki
DOB 8/8/1964
Place of Bith Des Moines, IA
/

I

In the event that there are fees, I would be grateful if you would inform me of the total charges in advance of fulfilling my request. I would prefer the request filled electronically, by e-mail attachment if available or CD-ROM if not.

Thank you in advance for your anticipated cooperation in this matter. I look forward to receiving your response to this request within 20 business days, as the statute requires.

Sincerely,

Janet Przewlocki
